The paper deals with compression and retrieval of multidimensional databases, which is a topic closely related to database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of Huffman coding and caching also involves information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a model for performance analysis, which could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications.
